OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 27 MAY
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1957FRobin Holmes presents a BBC TV
OL,7,Fnews programme for the final time.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1964FDuty news editor Fred Holtum
OL,10,Fpresents a Newsflash (BBC One) during
OL,11,Fthe morning, announcing the death of
OL,12,FIndian Prime Minister, Jawaharlal
OL,13,FNehru.
OL,14,
OL,15,FHoltum ended up fronting the bulletin
OL,16,Fas there were no news presenters or
OL,17,Freporters on duty at Alexandra Palace
OL,18,Fand because he was the only person with
OL,19,Fprevious broadcasting experience (in
OL,20,Fradio).
